21#ifndef _ELF_AVR_H
22#define _ELF_AVR_H
23
24#include "elf/reloc-macros.h"
25
26/* Processor specific flags for the ELF header e_flags field. */
27#define EF_AVR_MACH 0x7F
28
29/* If bit #7 is set, it is assumed that the elf file uses local symbols
30 as reference for the relocations so that linker relaxation is possible. */
31#define EF_AVR_LINKRELAX_PREPARED 0x80
32
33#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR1 1
34#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR2 2
35#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR25 25
36#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR3 3
37#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR31 31
38#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR35 35
39#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR4 4
40#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR5 5
41#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR51 51
42#define E_AVR_MACH_AVR6 6
43#define E_AVR_MACH_AVRTINY 100
44#define E_AVR_MACH_XMEGA1 101
45#define E_AVR_MACH_XMEGA2 102
46#define E_AVR_MACH_XMEGA3 103
47#define E_AVR_MACH_XMEGA4 104
48#define E_AVR_MACH_XMEGA5 105
49#define E_AVR_MACH_XMEGA6 106
50#define E_AVR_MACH_XMEGA7 107
51
52/* Relocations. */

60 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_LO8_LDI, 6)
61 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_HI8_LDI, 7)
62 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_HH8_LDI, 8)
63 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_LO8_LDI_NEG, 9)
64 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_HI8_LDI_NEG, 10)
65 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_HH8_LDI_NEG, 11)
66 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_LO8_LDI_PM, 12)
67 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_HI8_LDI_PM, 13)
68 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_HH8_LDI_PM, 14)
69 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_LO8_LDI_PM_NEG, 15)
70 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_HI8_LDI_PM_NEG, 16)

81 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_8_LO8, 27)
82 RELOC_NUMBER (R_AVR_8_HI8, 28)
